<h1 id="cc-title" class="text-center">Paladin</h1>

<h2 id="cc-subtitle" class="text-center mb-5">Oath of The Void</h2>

<p id="subclass-overview-text" class="text-left mx-5 mb-5 p-2 rounded"><i>To swear an Oath of The Void is swearing a
    commitment to serve the Undeath Queen. Bathe in the darkness of the Void, paladins who swear this oath will be
    shunned, chastised and feared by many. However, to be swayed by the ideals of those who can not see behind the veil
    is to be fragile, not what a messenger of the Queen is supposed to represent. You take this oath because you love
    and care for the world and its people and you are not afraid to fight evil corruption with your own darkness.</i>
</p>

<h1 id="ability-title" class="text-left ml-5">Tenets of The Void</h1>
<p id="ability-text" class="text-left mx-5">The tenets of the Void are held by paladins to safeguard the Void and
  prevent the balance between it and the material plane from collapsing.</p>
<ul class="text-left mx-5">
  <li>
    <p id="ability-text"><b>Some Secrets are Better Left Unknown</b>: Knowledge is power and it can do unimaginable
      damage. Keep safe the secrets of the Queenâ€™s domain.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p id="ability-text"><b>Loyalty to the Queen</b>: Do not be sway by gifts or favors. Stay true to your order as a
      servant of the Undeath Queen.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p id="ability-text"><b>No Mercy for the Uninvited</b>: You are what stands between invaders wanting to cross
      between The Void and other planes. Snuff them out, with extreme prejudice.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p id="ability-text"><b>Shine in the Dark</b>: Cutia is a kind soul and you should always greet with a smile for
      nothing is stronger in a time of despair.</p>
  </li>
</ul>

