<h1 id="ability-title" class="text-left ml-5">Channel Divinity: Void Field</h1>
<p id="ability-text" class="text-left mx-5 mb-3">As an action, you summon a 30ft radius cloud of Void darkness and
  heavily obscured the area that lasts for 10 minutes. You and any creatures you choose within 5ft of you can see
  normally in this darkness. Creatures within this zone will have to make attack rolls and Perception checks at
  disadvantage, even with Darkvision. While in this zone, your weapon deals an extra 1d4 necrotic damage and you are
  healed for the amount of necrotic damage dealt.</p>

<h1 id="ability-title" class="text-left ml-5">Channel Divinity: The Queen's Command</h1>
<p id="ability-text" class="text-left mx-5 mb-3">As a bonus action, select 1 Undead creature within 30ft of you that you
  can see. That creature must make a Wisdom saving throw or be charmed for 1 minute. This charm effect bypass the charm
  immunity if that creature has it. The creature can make the saving throw again at the end of each of its turn.</p>

